<l>tāmvīḻvār meṉṟōṭ ṭuyili ṉiṉitukol</l>
<l>tāmaraik kaṇṇā ṉulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Can the lotus-eyed Vishnu's heaven be indeed as sweet to those who delight to sleep in the delicate arms of their beloved ?</l>
